i-scam-call-detection-feature-io" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow">The Verge</a></b></p><p class="paragraph" style="text-align:left;">谷歌宣布推出一项新的 Android 功能，以防止使用 Gemini Nano 语言模型进行电话诈骗。这种设备上的通话监控工具将实时警告用户潜在的诈骗，并保持私密性。去年，全球有四分之一的人因诈骗损失超过 1 万亿美元，该功能的推出日期尚未确定。</p><p class="paragraph" style="text-align:left;"><b>重要度超过5.3的高报道新闻：</b></p><p class="paragraph" style="text-align:left;"> [5.8]普京因核机密泄露谣言清洗国防部<br>（ <a class="link" href="https://www.newsminimalist.com/articles/putin-purges-defense-ministry-amid-nuclear-secrets-leak-rumor-c13fc2b3" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow">新闻周刊+44</a> ）</p><p class="paragraph" style="text-align:left;"> [5.3]拜登提高对中国商品的关税，包括电动汽车和芯片<br>（ <a class="link" href="https://www.newsminimalist.com/articles/biden-raises-tariffs-on-chinese-goods-including-evs-and-chips-385857c0" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow">纽约时报+8</a> ）</p><p class="paragraph" style="text-align:left;"><b>想阅读更多内容吗？</b></p><p class="paragraph" style="text-align:left;">在<a class="link" href="http://newsminimalist.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow">newsminimalist.com</a>上查看更多新闻</p><hr class="content_break"><p class="paragraph" style="text-align:left;">感谢您的阅读，很快再见，</p><p class="paragraph" style="text-align:left;">瓦迪姆</p></div><div class='beehiiv__footer'><br class='beehiiv__footer__break'><hr class='beehiiv__footer__line'> <a target="_blank" class="beehiiv__footer_link" style="text-align: center;" href="https://www.beehiiv.com/?utm_campaign=16bcb8dc-6386-481d-b23d-20e767021ca5&utm_medium=post_rss&utm_source=news_minimalist">技术支持：beehiv</a></div></div> ;
